<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.8">
<l>kāṟaipū ṇuṅkaṇṇā ṭikāṇuntaṉ kaiyil vaḷaikulukkum</l>
<l>kūṟai yuṭukkumayark kuntaṅkov vaiccev vāytiruttum</l>
<l>tēṟittē ṟiniṉṟā yirampērttē vaṉtiṟam pitaṟṟum</l>
<l>māṟilmā maṇivaṇṇaṉ mēlivaḷ māluṟu kiṉṟāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She, who wears a golden necklace,</l>
<l rend="indent">looks in the mirror, shakes the bangles on her hand,</l>
<l>puts on [her] garments, becomes weak,</l>
<l rend="indent">arranging her kovvai red lips,</l>
<l>standing, gaining strength, babbles</l>
<l rend="indent">about the goodness of god [and his] thousand names,</l>
<l>has gone mad for the changeless, dark jewel hued [lord]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
